    "components": {
      "type": "array",
      "description": "Multiple components within a single asset.\n\nUse for:\n- Monorepo patterns (Nx, Turborepo, Lerna)\n- Multi-container applications\n- Microservices architectures\n- Micro-frontends\n\nComponents have symmetric provides/requires:\n- provides: What the component exposes (endpoints, routes, APIs)\n- requires: What the component depends on (other components, services, assets)\n",
